Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:10.64,Tema_Minmay,,0,0,0,,1, 2, 3, 4
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:10.64,Tema_Basara,,0,0,0,,1, 2, 3, 4
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:12.78,Tema_Minmay,,0,0,0,,1, 2, 3, 4
